This is one of the better Trinidadian West Indian restaurant. For most who don't know Jamaican and Trinidadian restaurants have different specialties. Examples being Jerk chicken is a Jamaican staple however Roti and Stew chicken are more of a Trinidadian thing. All in all test things out to see what you like best. There are many other countries in the Caribbean and while some borrow from others only tasting will tell you what you like.  Food taste are consistently good and authentic at Jen's.  Most West Indians know this is not always the case as well as professionalism but Jen's is well managed with a great staff that works quickly to take your order and they have consistent hours.
